<div class="archived-top-box">
<p><span style="font-size:150%;"><strong>THIS PAGE IS ARCHIVED</strong></span></p>
<p>The information on this page is not up-to-date, and/or has been replaced by other content.</p>
<p>It is preserved for historical purposes.</p>
<p><span style="font-size:90%;"><em>See <a href="/archived-scps">Archived Pages</a> for a detailed explanation of archival.</em></span></p>
</div>
<div class="archived-top-box">
<p>The new version of this page can be found <a href="/object-classes">here</a>.</p>
</div>
